Package com.irurueta.navigation.frames

Class ECIFrame

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.irurueta.navigation.frames.ECIorECEFFrame<ECIFrame>
      • com.irurueta.navigation.frames.ECIFrame
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Frame, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    public class ECIFrame
extends ECIorECEFFrame<ECIFrame>
    Contains position, velocity and coordinates transformation matrix expressed in ECI frame. Position and velocity of this frame is expressed along ECI axes as described here: FrameType.EARTH_CENTERED_INERTIAL_FRAME.
    See Also:
